"1/2 cup minced celery","1/2 cup minced green bell pepper","1/2 cup minced red bell pepper","1/2 cup 1/3-less-fat cream cheese","1/3 cup light mayonnaise","1 teaspoon curry powder","1 teaspoon hot sauce","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon grated lemon rind","1/4 teaspoon dry mustard","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","1 pound lump crabmeat, shell pieces removed","36  (1/4-inch-thick) slices diagonally cut French bread baguette (about 18 ounces)","1 tablespoon olive oil"